Terragator/Torca:
::Terragator sees a strange animal.  It looks like a cross between an 
Elephant and a whale.  It is Torca.  He transforms::
Terragator: That thing's a bot!  And a Maximal at that!  Terragator TERRORIZE!
::Torca notices him::
Torca: A Predacon!  State your name, creature.
Terragator: I am Terragator, you?
Torca: Torca
Terragator: Torca, eh?
::Takes out his fusion cannon::
Terragator: DIE!!!
::Torca dodges the attack, and takes out his dorsal gun, preparing to shoot::
Terragator: No more Torca.  Grant me mercy, I beg of you!
Torca: Please, that got my ancestor killed, I'm not falling for it.:)
